{"tid":1770604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"128 有不反！今次要有新意！試下整萬人移動砌圖？","createTime":"2019-12-05T10:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T10:31:46.000Z","uid":249040,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"32f080b5066724feaf332bca6c09c1ef02537618","tid":1770604,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:18:35.000Z","msg":"今次12.8係國際人權日主題， 要突顯人權被暴力蹂躝！ ！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />參考效果：<br />\n<br />\n羅馬尼亞連13天抗議 萬人國旗拼圖表訴求<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xgfBd21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxgfBd21.jpg&h=27efb3d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">印一張A4紙， 正面係一粒催淚彈， 背面 係其中一位犧牲左手足的歲數（數字字體要放到最大）。</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>嗌口號時候，擺張紙係頭頂， 拼成一幅移動砌圖， 比外媒係天橋影相！ </ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\">嗌有關狗嘅口號： 擺催淚彈個面係頭頂， 突出幾十萬人都被逼吸過催淚彈嘅主題 ！</span> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\">嗌其他口號/唱榮光個陣， 擺歲數個面係頭頂， 毋忘手足犧牲左嘅生命，繼續與烈士同行！ </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下面係資料方便大家印製： <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i8jm9xg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi8jm9xg.jpg&h=76d9c438&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n熊家俊先生(25歲)         15/12/2017<br />\n梁凌杰先生(35歲)          15/6/2019<br />\n盧曉欣小姐(21歲)          30/6/2019<br />\n鄔幸恩小姐(29歲)          30/6/2019<br />\n麥小姐(28歲)                    3/7/2019<br />\n梅先生(32歲)                    5/7/2019<br />\n范先生(26歲)                  22/7/2019<br />\n郭先生Calvin(25歲)       27/8/2019<br />\n姬先生(16歲)                    2/9/2019<br />\n陳彥霖小姐(15歲)           19/9/2019<br />\n曾穎欣小姐(26歲)           7/11/2019<br />\n周梓樂先生(22歲)           8/11/2019"},{"pid":"98214ea0b2b120804afc11666f1dc7221baf1529","tid":1770604,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:19:00.000Z","msg":"可以用其他催淚彈圖， 但要同催淚彈 色彩反差大d， 離遠先睇到！"},{"pid":"3185528f2d5d5e150d74db53fb1d43383b559494","tid":1770604,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1"},{"pid":"77ea21f42ef0547abccd29d71584208b6dd6319d","tid":1770604,"uid":73293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:19:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">128  維園見</span></span></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KsKuy8t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKsKuy8t.jpg&h=252ad633&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42rgYzb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42rgYzb.jpg&h=833df8cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0f4871f725f21e9273113fbe60e629c47301bbf","tid":1770604,"uid":249040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:19:45.000Z","msg":"大家點睇？"},{"pid":"631c82317eb066ff76d82cbb0704974a3018665a","tid":1770604,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:19:52.000Z","msg":"人哋喺國旗 你係圖片 難度有啲高 可改善"},{"pid":"a350e0298adfb33ec8186a8421fcae622af2c0f5","tid":1770604,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:20:21.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"a7c47e2cb8b37776d03dcc3f1010cfa5e7a736f6","tid":1770604,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"631c82317eb066ff76d82cbb0704974a3018665a","tid":1770604,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:19:52.000Z","msg":"人哋喺國旗 你係圖片 難度有啲高 可改善"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1